# Pulse Audio Controls
bindsym XF86AudioRaiseVolume exec amixer -q sset Master 1%+
bindsym Shift+XF86AudioRaiseVolume exec amixer -q sset Master 10%+
bindsym XF86AudioLowerVolume exec amixer -q sset Master 1%-
bindsym Shift+XF86AudioLowerVolume exec amixer -q sset Master 10%-
bindsym XF86AudioMute exec amixer -q sset Master toggle
bindsym XF86AudioPlay exec mpc toggle
bindsym XF86AudioPause exec mpc toggle
bindsym XF86AudioNext exec mpc next
bindsym XF86AudioPrev exec mpc prev

# Other
